Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.82,0:00:18.86,SeriesTitle,,0,0,0,,{\pos(334.133,309.733)\fad(150,270)}Brave{\fscx900} {\r}Exkaiser
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.87,0:00:24.54,SongOP,,0,0,0,,Over a million of them shine with a blue light
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.17,0:00:31.22,SongOP,,0,0,0,,The shards of love have scattered
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.63,0:00:38.22,SongOP,,0,0,0,,It's brewing in this world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.22,0:00:41.18,SongOP,,0,0,0,,A storm that you'll confront
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.18,0:00:44.73,SongOP,,0,0,0,,And because I believe in you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.98,0:00:49.65,SongOP,,0,0,0,,I'm not afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.86,0:00:53.86,SongOP,,0,0,0,,GO WITH ME Exkaiser
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.32,0:00:57.28,SongOP,,0,0,0,,Courage and friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.49,0:01:03.33,SongOP,,0,0,0,,That moment when we join our strength GATHER WAY
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.96,0:01:06.88,SongOP,,0,0,0,,GO WITH ME Exkaiser
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.25,0:01:10.25,SongOP,,0,0,0,,I'd almost forgotten it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.38,0:01:18.60,SongOP,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-0.3\q2}The fiery burning and important PASSIONATE feeling in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.47,0:01:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The mysterious and vast universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.95,0:01:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,In this universe exists the evil life forms, \Nthe space pirates Geisters
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.58,0:01:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,who've invaded Earth in order to obtain the treasures of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.50,0:01:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,However, in front of the Geisters who use destruction and plunder as they wish
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.58,0:01:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,a hero appeared, who completely stood in their way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.93,0:02:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the cosmic police, Exkaiser.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.83,0:02:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the story of Brave Exkaiser and his friends, who fight against evil all around the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.48,0:02:18.82,EpisodeTitle,,0,0,0,,The Pharmacy is Empty!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.28,0:02:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,"Mysterious Robot Attacks Rocket"!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.50,0:02:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.53,0:02:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't a grade school newspaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.15,0:02:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.33,0:02:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you see them as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.21,0:02:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You blockhead!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.23,0:02:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you that unless we have a photographic proof, I don't want it in the newspaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.88,0:02:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But my camera was--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.05,0:02:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! I've had it with your excuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.92,0:02:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time this happens, I'll take three months of your pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.99,0:02:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right... I'm on the short end of the stick...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.34,0:02:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Never give up! Scoop is my name, and scoop is my game!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.48,0:02:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,MAGMA MAGMA MAGMA MAGMA MAGMA
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.21,0:03:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And if I have these, I'll be number one in Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.45,0:03:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Very Very Power Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.77,0:03:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Joanna...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.94,0:03:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.55,0:03:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's getting better...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.16,0:03:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,-Please! Let this pass!\N-If we keep doing like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.07,0:03:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you jerks! How long are you going to sit around!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.34,0:03:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.69,0:03:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,...is what Dino Geist-sama told me to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.19,0:03:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't he instruct us to gather information on this planet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.06,0:03:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yeah, that's why we stole TVs first--hmm?\N-When you're feeling down...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.58,0:03:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,...take Magma Drink and Power Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.96,0:03:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Very Very!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.03,0:03:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Power Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.26,0:03:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Very Very!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.46,0:03:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Gulp gulp gulp gulp gulp
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.42,0:03:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Magma Power!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.88,0:03:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Take Magma Drink and Very Very Power Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.06,0:04:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, if we had that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.46,0:04:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and we'd be Very Very Power Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.55,0:04:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's go get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.83,0:04:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh!? Onee-chan caught a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.40,0:04:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama, bring me more covers!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.70,0:04:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Shouldn't you be cooling down?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.65,0:04:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool down? That's nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.83,0:04:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help it that I'm shivering with cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.58,0:04:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I should call the doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.09,0:04:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine! When you catch cold, you'd better stay warm and sweat a lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.02,0:04:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and that will bring down the fever and lessen my weight, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.40,0:04:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind that! Just bring me more covers!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.33,0:04:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Just drink up your medicine
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.07,0:04:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.62,0:04:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Only three more kilos...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.82,0:04:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan, are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.09,0:05:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to this, I'm skipping school and dieting at once! Two birds with one stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.69,0:05:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't dare give up this opportunity!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.37,0:05:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what this is about...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.31,0:05:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.15,0:05:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hold it right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.79,0:05:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna help me with my diet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.76,0:05:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, pretend you're a hot-water bottle...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.16,0:05:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.87,0:05:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, move it! You're gonna make me late!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.95,0:05:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it not working again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.11,0:05:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouta, can you kick it from behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.75,0:05:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe that'll help it move.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.06,0:05:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa, doing that will get you nowhere! Even cars might have feelings!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.51,0:05:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it! Just get in!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.78,0:05:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa doesn't mean any harm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.45,0:05:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He really likes this car, so he wants you to keep up with the good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.15,0:05:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.59,0:05:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.57,0:05:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... Even cars have feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.06,0:06:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, this is the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.49,0:06:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.76,0:06:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamai Pharmacy
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.85,0:06:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Earthquake!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.12,0:06:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Earthquake!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.33,0:06:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Nothing's shaking...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.56,0:06:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.18,0:06:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.13,0:06:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.34,0:06:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Class is cancelled today since more than half of the class called in sick--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.38,0:06:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and our class is closing down for the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.75,0:06:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So I ask you to study at home--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.56,0:07:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess Kotomi-chan is sick, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.97,0:07:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I see it's true what they say, that the stupid never fall ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.96,0:07:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really? And aren't you as bright as day!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.28,0:07:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The cook at my estate creates nothing but A1 healthy meals.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.44,0:07:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, we have direct access to all the herbal medicines straight from the origin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.42,0:07:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm far different from you commoners.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.87,0:07:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, I should pay Kotomi-chan a visit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.95,0:07:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.88,0:07:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotomi, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.17,0:07:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotomi-chan! Are you alright!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.85,0:07:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouta...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.11,0:07:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,She suddenly fell ill with a fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.73,0:07:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A fever?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.66,0:07:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, you're in the way..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.34,0:08:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Scoop... Scoop... Scoop... Scoop...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.18,0:08:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokuda-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.27,0:08:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Kouta-kun? You look down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.21,0:08:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... down...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.86,0:08:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right! That drink you got! You said it would cure colds and everything, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.27,0:08:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you mean that Magma Drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.04,0:08:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! I could use one of those!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.01,0:08:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I think you can buy them at the pharmacy over-- huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.59,0:08:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.93,0:08:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.69,0:08:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.55,0:08:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a scoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.04,0:08:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Power Up! Power Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.78,0:09:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is the editorial department of Touto Newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.91,0:09:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief! It's a scoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.41,0:09:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world is going on!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.06,0:09:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a medicine thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.40,0:09:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Moreover, they're taking the whole store!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.99,0:09:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Drugstores are falling down as if they're being eaten from inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.10,0:09:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahhhh, there goes another one!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.83,0:09:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the eighth one! Every drugstore in the vicinity is under attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.33,0:09:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokuda, you aren't sleepwalking again, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.49,0:09:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief! This is a real scoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.91,0:09:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet some alien race fell sick and has to steal all our medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.41,0:09:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You weren't doing your job and watched some sci-fi videos, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.97,0:09:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief! I'm not lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.31,0:09:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Moron! No human could plow through the Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.79,0:09:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Drugstore? Something humans can't do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.42,0:09:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.29,0:09:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.16,0:09:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't feel anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.65,0:09:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be! Maybe we should drink more!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.05,0:09:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, gimme one!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.90,0:09:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Screw you! I stole these.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.85,0:10:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to try one for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.99,0:10:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone as brainless as you probably doesn't have anything to power up...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.85,0:10:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.81,0:10:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If you end up drinking all the treasures,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.57,0:10:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,that won't get us anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.17,0:10:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,...is what Dino Geist-sama said.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.01,0:10:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Dino Geist-sama has an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.00,0:10:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Take much more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.67,0:10:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There must be a location where they create such things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.45,0:10:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I see! And that's why he's the boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.34,0:10:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave this one to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.27,0:10:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Asahidai General Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.55,0:11:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Nurse, will Kotomi-chan be alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.22,0:11:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! As long as she takes her medicine and gets plenty of rest, she'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.89,0:11:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But all the drugstores in the city were attacked...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.86,0:11:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a drugstore in the hospital, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.95,0:11:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There is?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.16,0:11:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.37,0:11:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuuko! Fuuko! Fuuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.10,0:11:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuuko! Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.69,0:11:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa? What about your work?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.43,0:11:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I was told that Fuuko was brought to the hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.66,0:11:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a simple cold. Looks like she overheated herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.86,0:11:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Diet... Only 3 more kilograms...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.05,0:11:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuuko, get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.53,0:11:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The pharmacy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.45,0:11:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh!? This was where the medicine was!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.46,0:11:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How could this happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.97,0:11:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any way to replenish the medicine in storage?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.43,0:11:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea, but every pharmacy that supplies us hasn't re-stocked yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.95,0:12:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Then what about Kotomi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.18,0:12:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn those Geisters...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.50,0:12:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sky Max! I'm checking out every location hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.39,0:12:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lag behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.40,0:12:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha! You're one to talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.58,0:12:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This type of situation is definitely the work of the Geisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.45,0:12:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems they're after this "medicine" thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.95,0:12:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Every place selling that was completely wiped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.35,0:12:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So that leaves us with the source of the medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.67,0:12:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouta...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.97,0:12:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Exkaiser! Take me to the pharmaceutical plant!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.14,0:12:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,To the pharmaceutical plant?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.50,0:12:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to get medicine. Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.32,0:12:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.69,0:13:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.69,0:13:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. I'm sure the Geisters will attack the pharmaceutical plant.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.70,0:13:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You can take care of the Geisters, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.90,0:13:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't get the medicine, Kotomi-chan might die!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.19,0:13:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Exkaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.05,0:13:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Exkaiser...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.42,0:13:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This boy knows who we are?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.65,0:13:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Exkaiser?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.03,0:13:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He is my comrade, Dash Max.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.01,0:13:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.54,0:13:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy! Leave this to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.06,0:13:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Exkaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.75,0:13:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, get in..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.59,0:13:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,From the pharmacy to the hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.48,0:13:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet they'll hit the pharmaceutical plant next.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.78,0:13:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, what a brilliant deduction!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.90,0:13:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should become a detective instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.70,0:14:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,They really came!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.67,0:14:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So, which one is the Very Very Power Up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.74,0:14:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Screw this! We'll take 'em all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.50,0:14:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Rip 'em all off!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.21,0:14:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.91,0:14:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a scoop! It's a scoop! Scoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.15,0:15:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,All the medicine is being stolen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.13,0:15:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Exkaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.18,0:15:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-All right! We know what to do!\N-Boy, leave this to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.02,0:15:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Change, Exkaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.94,0:15:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Change, Dash Max!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.36,0:15:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Geisters! We Kaisers will not allow you to proceed with your evil plans!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.59,0:15:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Exkaiser! You had to show up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.76,0:15:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I have crossed the galaxy to capture all of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.91,0:15:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.55,0:16:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.13,0:16:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't think we'll come quietly...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.63,0:16:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, make your move!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.42,0:16:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, here we come... Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.94,0:16:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Exkaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.71,0:16:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,-Now's our chance.\N-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.46,0:16:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No! The medicine tank!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.10,0:16:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Exkaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.21,0:16:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Exkaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.53,0:17:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.63,0:17:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Change, Sky Max!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.55,0:17:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a bit more for my scoop! Scoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.62,0:17:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that we're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.78,0:17:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean? You saved us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.06,0:17:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave this one to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.09,0:17:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Take care of it, Exkaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.59,0:17:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Drill Max! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.19,0:17:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.48,0:18:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey now! You'll fight with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.46,0:18:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Change, Drill Max!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.83,0:18:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The Max Team assembles!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.38,0:18:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Screw you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.81,0:18:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Max Team, Form Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.81,0:19:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Triple Fusion, God Max!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.19,0:19:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! Get those Geisters!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.93,0:19:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! The scoop turned into a bigger scoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.53,0:19:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,All of you're going down altogether! Get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.14,0:19:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm next in the ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.26,0:19:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Exkaiser! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.96,0:19:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,King Loader!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.74,0:20:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Giant Fusion, King Exkaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.25,0:20:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaiser Sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.70,0:21:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thunder Flash!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.38,0:21:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.93,0:21:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.77,0:21:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally took it! I finally got a scoop! Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.89,0:21:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a rain of Magma Drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.13,0:21:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it pouring out for my celebration?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.91,0:21:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,-Kouta! Hurry and get the medicine.\N-I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.91,0:21:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor! Here's the medicine!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.19,0:22:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you! That will just do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.30,0:22:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,-Give this to Kotomi-chan.\N-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.12,0:22:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Now everyone should be safe thanks to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.37,0:22:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be worried about Fuuko-san as well..
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.97,0:22:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right! My sister was brought here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.78,0:22:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need any medicine... My diet...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.33,0:22:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! I gained!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.37,0:22:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally got a scoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.12,0:22:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.97,0:22:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What!? It didn't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.14,0:22:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.11,0:22:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I failed again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.18,0:22:56.18,SongED,,0,0,0,,Faraway wind carries your dream
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.18,0:23:05.28,SongED,,0,0,0,,What could you discover from this excited feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.99,0:23:15.33,SongED,,0,0,0,,Dreams get bigger strongly and fast
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.33,0:23:22.96,SongED,,0,0,0,,Don't forget to be who you are
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.00,0:23:31.26,SongED,,0,0,0,,Embrace your enthusiastic heart
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.26,0:23:39.27,SongED,,0,0,0,,And try walking that path
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.50,0:23:46.27,NextEpisodePreview,,0,0,0,,{\pos(325.344,314.667)}NEXT EPISODE PREVIEW
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.23,0:23:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on a date with Kotomi-chan in a submarine!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.08,0:23:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're gonna see a sunken ship that's full of treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.10,0:23:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that romantic?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.94,0:23:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Uwah! The Geisters again!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.82,0:24:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! They're causing an undersea eruption!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.41,0:24:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,On the next episode of Brave Exkaiser,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.18,0:24:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Our Sunken Ship Expedition Party
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.45,0:24:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there an alien in your home, too?
